---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ExperienceCatalogue from '../components/ExperienceCatalogue.astro';
const heroImage = '/images/amazon-river-hero.png';
---
<BaseLayout title="Águia Amazonas" description="Private and small-group Amazon rainforest journeys from Manaus with Antonio, your guide, working closely with the local community." image={heroImage}>
  <section class="hero" style={`--hero:url('${heroImage}')`}>
    <div class="hero-shade"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="eyebrow light">Born in the Amazon · Guiding since 2003</p>
      <h1>Go beyond<br/><em>the known.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">Personal rainforest journeys, river expeditions and survival experiences led by Antonio, who calls the Amazon home.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="#experiences">Find your journey</a>
        <a class="button ghost" href="https://wa.me/5592994587173?text=Hello%20Antonio%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20plan%20an%20Amazon%20journey." target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Ask Antonio</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-note"><span>03°06′S</span><p>Manaus is the gateway.<br/>The forest is the destination.</p></div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro wrap">
    <div><p class="eyebrow">Not a packaged holiday</p><h2>Amazon travel<br/>with a human pulse.</h2></div>
    <div class="intro-copy"><p>Águia Amazonas creates intimate journeys for travellers who want to understand the forest—not simply pass through it.</p><p>Every route is shaped by the river, the season and you. Antonio works closely with the local community to create experiences rooted in life here.</p></div>
  </section>

  <ExperienceCatalogue />

  <section class="guide-promo">
    <img src="/images/home/travel-guide-flooded-forest.webp" alt="View from a canoe entering the seasonally flooded Amazon forest" loading="lazy" />
    <div><p class="eyebrow light">Plan before you travel</p><h2>Understand the forest before you enter it.</h2><p>Water levels transform the landscape throughout the year. Learn when to visit, what to pack and which kind of Amazon journey suits you.</p><a class="button primary" href="/brazilian-amazon-travel-guide/">Read the Brazilian Amazon guide</a></div>
  </section>

  <section class="antonio-band">
    <div class="antonio-portrait"><img src="/images/people/antonio.webp" alt="Antonio, founder of Águia Amazonas" /><span>ANTONIO</span></div>
    <div class="antonio-copy"><p class="eyebrow light">Your host in the Amazon</p><blockquote>“This is my home and my life’s work. I want you to experience it with respect, curiosity and wonder.”</blockquote><p>Antonio · Founder and expedition guide</p><a class="text-link" href="/about/">Meet the people behind the journey →</a></div>
  </section>

  <section class="promise wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">The Águia way</p>
    <div class="promise-grid"><div><b>01</b><h3>Local by nature</h3><p>Antonio’s lived knowledge and close relationship with the local community—not a rehearsed script.</p></div><div><b>02</b><h3>Small by design</h3><p>Private and small-group travel makes room for real encounters and lighter footprints.</p></div><div><b>03</b><h3>Season-led</h3><p>Routes adapt to water levels, weather and wildlife. The forest always has the final word.</p></div></div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .guide-promo{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;background:#08261e;color:#fff}.guide-promo img{width:100%;height:100%;min-height:480px;object-fit:cover}.guide-promo>div{padding:70px 7vw;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}.guide-promo h2{font-family:var(--display);font-size:clamp(42px,5vw,72px);line-height:1.02;margin:0 0 20px}.guide-promo>div>p:not(.eyebrow){color:#c6d6cf;font-size:18px}.guide-promo .button{align-self:flex-start;margin-top:18px}@media(max-width:900px){.guide-promo{grid-template-columns:1fr}.guide-promo img{min-height:320px}.guide-promo>div{padding:50px 24px}}
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
